---
import Contact from '../../components/Contact.astro';
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import aboutTitle from '../../assets/about.svg';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import backgroundImage from '../../assets/0233f2c4c9a0817f3a88064a357678647bb97e85.png';
import developersImage from '../../assets/developers.png';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div
    class="flex w-full flex-col gap-32 py-24 items-center md:px-32"
    style={{
      backgroundImage: `url(${backgroundImage.src})`,
      backgroundSize: 'cover',
      backgroundPosition: 'center',
    }}
  >
    <div class="mx-auto w-full flex flex-col justify-center gap-12 text-center">
      <Image
        src={aboutTitle}
        alt="about title"
        class="mx-auto w-1/5 aspect-auto"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-lg text-white md:mx-24 md:text-2xl text-left font-light"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-0">
        <Image
          src={developersImage}
          alt="developers talking image"
          class="w-full md:w-2/5 h-auto object-cover shrink-0 rounded-lg"
        />
        <div
          class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-8 py-6 mx-4 md:mx-0 md:px-4 md:py-0"
        >
          <p class="">
            The Arm ecosystem has grown far beyond mobile, now spanning AI,
            cloud, edge, automotive, and client compute. As the ecosystem has
            expanded and technology evolved, software complexity has increased.
            No single company can maintain enablement alone - open source
            collaboration is key.
          </p>
          <p>
            <span class="text-cc-cyan">CoreCollective </span>provides a neutral
            platform for innovators in the Arm ecosystem to come together and
            openly collaborate on common requirements. By working together on
            the common needs once, companies can focus more of their efforts and
            resources on differentiating their product.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-4 lg:mx-auto flex flex-col gap-8">
        <p class="font-extrabold">
          The Core Collective comprises multiple Working Groups, each focused on
          a specific <br />technology. Any company is free to join and
          participate in the CoreCollective.
        </p>
        <p>
          To better understand options to join, as well as enhancing your
          membership <br />to increase visibility and influence <a
            class="text-cc-cyan"
            href="/join">click here.</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>
          To see the benefits of joining as well as the current active Working
          Groups, <br />please download our <a
            class="text-cc-cyan no-underline"
            href="https://static-core-collective.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/assets/CoreCollective+Pitch+Deck+v1.2.pdf"
            target="_blank">short slide deck</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <Contact />
</BaseLayout>
